{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't really have too many-- too many-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] didn't know too much about it, because everything was very secretive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no press-- it was forbidden to write anything about it-- or radios or anything like it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was rumors what we heard from people here and there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- everything was in an uproar in those days, in 1944, '45.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, between 1940-- June-- between the times that the Russians came in in 1944 and liberated us-- we were-- we-- we were-- we felt that the Russians liberated us-- to the time that, you know, the end of the war, to V Day, so there wasn't that much of a transition in our lives right in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people really didn't know too much about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We heard rumors here and there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were underground letters that came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's how the Aliyah Bet was formed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now Schmuel was very active in that movement, and he was a very close friend of my aunt's, and in fact he was a professor and he would come and he would really help me with my studies as well, so I was very close to him.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was-- I would say-- I was 14-- 14.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was-- must have been in like those days about 28, 25, something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And again, I looked up to him as a man, you know, for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- perhaps then a little bit maybe, but he was always very kind to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he would help me with everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he wanted to take my whole family out, my aunt and uncle, underground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in those days we used to call them transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were many transports that left Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
